
going into my parents room i yawed catching dads attention making him turn around ,"hey" i said softly.
dad mummbled something and i said ,"what?" he mummbled something again...
i should have known this was going to happen.,"what?" he said i rolled my eyes
,"what?" i asked. ,"what??" dad asked. i threw my hands up and said ,"nevermind!!" and walked out of the room.
this family need hearing aids...